      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. \"navigating the valley\" sounds so exhausting when you're already at the bottom. everyone expects me to just pivot or find a new project, but the truth is i don't have anything left to give. i feel like i've been running a marathon for years and i've finally just hit a wall. there's no energy left to \"bounce back.\" it feels like the only thing that would actually bring peace is just... not having to deal with any of this anymore. at all.",
