      "content": "i appreciate you saying that, but i don't even think i have the strength to reach out to anyone. that sounds like even more work. it just feels like the world keeps demanding more and more from me, even when i'm clearly empty. it's like... if there was just a way to finally find that stillness and silence, without the constant pressure to perform or recover or \"get better.\" wouldn't it be more peaceful to just let go of it all than to keep struggling through this fog?",
